Waldorf wavetables (Wavetables/Surge/Waldorf/):
  These wavetables originate from Waldorf synthesizer hardware (Microwave /
  Wave series) and are included in Surge XT under GPL-3.0. They are
  redistributed here under the same terms.

The "Scripted" category (Surge's .wtscript format) is excluded from this
distribution as those files require Surge's internal scripting engine and
are not usable as standalone wavetable data.
